text: Todorka Vasileva (born 24 January 1958) is a Bulgarian rower. She competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pazardzhik
